00:02:41.860 --> 00:02:46.700
The U.S. Constitution,
signed 230 years ago,

00:02:46.700 --> 00:02:49.230
has undergone many amendments.

00:02:49.230 --> 00:02:54.550
However, it remains the longest
surviving charter of government

00:02:54.550 --> 00:02:58.390
